    "synopsis": "Deep within Imperium Nihilus, in the shadow of the Great Rift, Blood Angels Chief Librarian Mephiston and his comrades are drawn by cryptic visions to a war-torn world. There the sorcerers of the Thousand Sons labour to unite nine Silver Towers and complete a ritual that would empower their daemon-primarch Magnus the Red and cast the entire sub-sector into Chaos. Having already endured the Devastation of Baal, Mephiston must summon all his strength and will to stop them — confronting a hidden truth that threatens to expose him to his darkest fears. The climactic battle of the Lord of Death's darkest hour.",
